      <title>Linux Bridge</title>
      <link href="/posts/7f213e49.html"/>
      <url>/posts/7f213e49.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Bridge 是 Linux 下实现虚拟交换机设备的实现，其工作原理同现实交换机基本一致。这里简单罗列了下基本的使用，然后通过两个案例模拟了对比传统交换机的配置。</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="操作-Bridge"><a href="#操作-Bridge" class="headerlink" title="操作 Bridge"></a>操作 Bridge</h1><h2 id="安装依赖工具"><a href="#安装依赖工具" class="headerlink" title="安装依赖工具"></a>安装依赖工具</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install bridge-utils</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加一个-Bridge"><a href="#添加一个-Bridge" class="headerlink" title="添加一个 Bridge"></a>添加一个 Bridge</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brctl addbr br1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="查看已有-Bridge"><a href="#查看已有-Bridge" class="headerlink" title="查看已有 Bridge"></a>查看已有 Bridge</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brctl show</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="将-veth-插入-Bridge"><a href="#将-veth-插入-Bridge" class="headerlink" title="将 veth 插入 Bridge"></a>将 veth 插入 Bridge</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brctl delif br1 veth1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="将-veth-从-Bridge-移除"><a href="#将-veth-从-Bridge-移除" class="headerlink" title="将 veth 从 Bridge 移除"></a>将 veth 从 Bridge 移除</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brctl delif br1 veth1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="删除-Bridge"><a href="#删除-Bridge" class="headerlink" title="删除 Bridge"></a>删除 Bridge</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brctl delbr br1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="实践测试"><a href="#实践测试" class="headerlink" title="实践测试"></a>实践测试</h1><h2 id="Bridge-实现主机互联互通"><a href="#Bridge-实现主机互联互通" class="headerlink" title="Bridge 实现主机互联互通"></a>Bridge 实现主机互联互通</h2><h3 id="拓扑"><a href="#拓扑" class="headerlink" title="拓扑"></a>拓扑</h3><p>三台主机使用交换机设备进行互联互通，主机使用网络名称空间模拟，交换机使用 Bridge模拟。</p><p><img src="/../images/Linux-Bridge/image-20220117152443335.png" alt="image-20220117152443335"></p><h3 id="配置过程"><a href="#配置过程" class="headerlink" title="配置过程"></a>配置过程</h3><h4 id="创建-Bridge-BR1-并启用"><a href="#创建-Bridge-BR1-并启用" class="headerlink" title="创建 Bridge BR1 并启用"></a>创建 Bridge BR1 并启用</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brctl addbr BR1</span><br><span class="line">ip link set dev BR1 up</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="创建终端"><a href="#创建终端" class="headerlink" title="创建终端"></a>创建终端</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip netns add ns1</span><br><span class="line">ip netns add ns2</span><br><span class="line">ip netns add ns3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="创建-VethPair"><a href="#创建-VethPair" class="headerlink" title="创建 VethPair"></a>创建 VethPair</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip link add veth1 type veth peer name veth11</span><br><span class="line">ip link add veth2 type veth peer name veth22</span><br><span class="line">ip link add veth3 type veth peer name veth33</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="按拓扑通过-VethPair-将设备互联"><a href="#按拓扑通过-VethPair-将设备互联" class="headerlink" title="按拓扑通过 VethPair 将设备互联"></a>按拓扑通过 VethPair 将设备互联</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip link set dev veth11 netns ns1</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns1 ip link set dev veth11 up</span><br><span class="line">ip link set dev veth22 netns ns2</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns2 ip link set dev veth22 up</span><br><span class="line">ip link set dev veth33 netns ns3</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns3 ip link set dev veth33 up</span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth1 up</span><br><span class="line">brctl addif BR1 veth1</span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth2 up</span><br><span class="line">brctl addif BR1 veth2</span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth3 up</span><br><span class="line">brctl addif BR1 veth3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="给-veth-配置-IP"><a href="#给-veth-配置-IP" class="headerlink" title="给 veth 配置 IP"></a>给 veth 配置 IP</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip netns exec ns1 ip addr add 10.0.1.1/24 dev veth11</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns2 ip addr add 10.0.1.2/24 dev veth22</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns3 ip addr add 10.0.1.3/24 dev veth33</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="测试"><a href="#测试" class="headerlink" title="测试"></a>测试</h3><p>直接互 ping 进行测试</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# ip netns exec ns1 ping 10.0.1.3 -c 2</span><br><span class="line">PING 10.0.1.3 (10.0.1.3) 56(84) bytes of data.</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 10.0.1.3: icmp_seq=1 ttl=64 time=0.090 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 10.0.1.3: icmp_seq=2 ttl=64 time=0.068 ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="通信抓包"><a href="#通信抓包" class="headerlink" title="通信抓包"></a>通信抓包</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# tcpdump -i veth3 -nn</span><br><span class="line">tcpdump: verbose output suppressed, use -v or -vv for full protocol decode</span><br><span class="line">listening on veth3, link-type EN10MB (Ethernet), capture size 262144 bytes</span><br><span class="line">11:05:30.660457 ARP, Request who-has 10.0.1.3 tell 10.0.1.1, length 28</span><br><span class="line">11:05:30.660473 ARP, Reply 10.0.1.3 is-at 1a:16:88:9f:f1:c8, length 28</span><br><span class="line">11:05:30.660479 IP 10.0.1.1 &gt; 10.0.1.3: ICMP echo request, id 1325, seq 1, length 64</span><br><span class="line">11:05:30.660504 IP 10.0.1.3 &gt; 10.0.1.1: ICMP echo reply, id 1325, seq 1, length 64</span><br><span class="line">11:05:31.700612 IP 10.0.1.1 &gt; 10.0.1.3: ICMP echo request, id 1325, seq 2, length 64</span><br><span class="line">11:05:31.700632 IP 10.0.1.3 &gt; 10.0.1.1: ICMP echo reply, id 1325, seq 2, length 64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="实现-vlan-隔离"><a href="#实现-vlan-隔离" class="headerlink" title="实现 vlan 隔离"></a>实现 vlan 隔离</h2><h3 id="拓扑-1"><a href="#拓扑-1" class="headerlink" title="拓扑"></a>拓扑</h3><p>两台主机连接至不同的交换机，实现互联互通。 交换机间的链路为Trunk，并且允许vlan10通过。</p><p><img src="/../images/Linux-Bridge/image-20220117152356933.png" alt="image-20220117152356933"></p><h3 id="配置过程-1"><a href="#配置过程-1" class="headerlink" title="配置过程"></a>配置过程</h3><p>这里使用 iproute2这个库</p><h4 id="创建交换机并开启-vlan-filter-功能"><a href="#创建交换机并开启-vlan-filter-功能" class="headerlink" title="创建交换机并开启 vlan filter 功能"></a>创建交换机并开启 vlan filter 功能</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip link add BR1 type bridge</span><br><span class="line">ip link set BR1 up</span><br><span class="line">ip link set dev BR1 type bridge vlan_filtering 1</span><br><span class="line">ip link add BR2 type bridge</span><br><span class="line">ip link set BR2 up</span><br><span class="line">ip link set dev BR2 type bridge vlan_filtering 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="创建终端和-VethPair"><a href="#创建终端和-VethPair" class="headerlink" title="创建终端和 VethPair"></a>创建终端和 VethPair</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip netns add ns1</span><br><span class="line">ip netns add ns2</span><br><span class="line">#</span><br><span class="line">ip link add veth1 type veth peer name veth11</span><br><span class="line">ip link add veth2 type veth peer name veth22</span><br><span class="line">ip link add veth12 type veth peer name veth21</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="按拓扑连接设备"><a href="#按拓扑连接设备" class="headerlink" title="按拓扑连接设备"></a>按拓扑连接设备</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip link set dev veth11 netns ns1</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns1 ip link set veth11 up</span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns1 ip addr add 10.0.1.1/24 dev veth11</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">ip <span class="built_in">link</span> <span class="built_in">set</span> dev veth22 netns ns2</span></span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns2 ip link set veth22 up </span><br><span class="line">ip netns exec ns2 ip addr add 10.0.1.2/24 dev veth22</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="进行交换机配置"><a href="#进行交换机配置" class="headerlink" title="进行交换机配置"></a>进行交换机配置</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip link set veth1 master BR1                   # 将 veth 插入交换机</span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth1 up                           # 启用 veth</span><br><span class="line">bridge vlan add dev veth1 vid 10 pvid untagged # 将 vlan10 的 tag 剥离并发送出去</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">ip <span class="built_in">link</span> <span class="built_in">set</span> veth2 master BR2</span></span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth2 up</span><br><span class="line">bridge vlan add dev veth2 vid 10 pvid untagged</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">ip <span class="built_in">link</span> <span class="built_in">set</span> veth12 master BR1</span></span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth12 up</span><br><span class="line">bridge vlan add vid 2-4094 dev veth12  # 设置端口为 trunk 允许 vlan 2-4094 通过</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">ip <span class="built_in">link</span> <span class="built_in">set</span> veth21 master BR2</span></span><br><span class="line">ip link set veth21 up</span><br><span class="line">bridge vlan add vid 2-4094 dev veth21</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看配置"><a href="#查看配置" class="headerlink" title="查看配置"></a>查看配置</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# bridge -c vlan show</span><br><span class="line">portvlan ids</span><br><span class="line">BR1 1 PVID Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">BR2 1 PVID Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">veth1 1 Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"> 10 PVID Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">veth2 1 Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"> 10 PVID Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">veth21 1 PVID Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"> 2-4094</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">veth12 1 PVID Egress Untagged</span><br><span class="line"> 2-4094</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="测试-1"><a href="#测试-1" class="headerlink" title="测试"></a>测试</h3><p>进行互 ping 测试</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# ip netns exec ns1 ping 10.0.1.2 -c 2</span><br><span class="line">PING 10.0.1.2 (10.0.1.2) 56(84) bytes of data.</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 10.0.1.2: icmp_seq=1 ttl=64 time=0.119 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 10.0.1.2: icmp_seq=2 ttl=64 time=0.047 ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="通信抓包-1"><a href="#通信抓包-1" class="headerlink" title="通信抓包"></a>通信抓包</h3><p> 在veth12抓包分析，报文带tag则成功</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# tcpdump -i veth12 -ne</span><br><span class="line">tcpdump: verbose output suppressed, use -v or -vv for full protocol decode</span><br><span class="line">listening on veth12, link-type EN10MB (Ethernet), capture size 262144 bytes</span><br><span class="line">10:59:23.576557 b2:82:aa:ee:05:05 &gt; Broadcast, ethertype 802.1Q (0x8100), length 46: vlan 10, p 0, ethertype ARP, Request who-has 10.0.1.2 tell 10.0.1.1, length 28</span><br><span class="line">10:59:23.576587 62:0d:66:a9:41:b2 &gt; b2:82:aa:ee:05:05, ethertype 802.1Q (0x8100), length 46: vlan 10, p 0, ethertype ARP, Reply 10.0.1.2 is-at 62:0d:66:a9:41:b2, length 28</span><br><span class="line">10:59:23.576593 b2:82:aa:ee:05:05 &gt; 62:0d:66:a9:41:b2, ethertype 802.1Q (0x8100), length 102: vlan 10, p 0, ethertype IPv4, 10.0.1.1 &gt; 10.0.1.2: ICMP echo request, id 1211, seq 1, length 64</span><br><span class="line">10:59:23.576619 62:0d:66:a9:41:b2 &gt; b2:82:aa:ee:05:05, ethertype 802.1Q (0x8100), length 102: vlan 10, p 0, ethertype IPv4, 10.0.1.2 &gt; 10.0.1.1: ICMP echo reply, id 1211, seq 1, length 64</span><br><span class="line">10:59:24.597118 b2:82:aa:ee:05:05 &gt; 62:0d:66:a9:41:b2, ethertype 802.1Q (0x8100), length 102: vlan 10, p 0, ethertype IPv4, 10.0.1.1 &gt; 10.0.1.2: ICMP echo request, id 1211, seq 2, length 64</span><br><span class="line">10:59:24.597137 62:0d:66:a9:41:b2 &gt; b2:82:aa:ee:05:05, ethertype 802.1Q (0x8100), length 102: vlan 10, p 0, ethertype IPv4, 10.0.1.2 &gt; 10.0.1.1: ICMP echo reply, id 1211, seq 2, length 64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
